divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home, when I saw the object which I noticed first for its bright lights. I first thought that the object might be a star. But I noticed that the object would move around ever so little. The object also had lights that would turn on and off. I went inside after I had finished my activity outside.
Summary: One hovering object, sparkling lights, which penny
